Filter and summarize the top 5 articles from this social media feed that have the highest viral potential or significance for a technically-minded audience.

* GUARDRAILS
Output as JSON with the following structure:
- articles: An array of objects, each containing:
    - title: The headline of the article
    - summary: A concise one-sentence description
    - viral_reason: Why this article is significant or potentially viral
    - url: An href for the article.  Simply use the text "Link", and set the URL to be the main URL of the article.
- meta:
    - total_reviewed: Count of articles processed
    - feed_name: "General Cloud"
